1. Klopka se ne vidi dok se u nju ne uhvatiš. (*zamka*) (You can't see the trap until you fall into it.)
2. Lovac je postavio *zamku* za divlje svinje. (The hunter set a trap for wild boars.)
3. Moramo biti oprezni, postoji *zamka* u svakom kutku. (We must be careful, there's a trap in every corner.)
4. Psi su upali u *zamku* i sada ne mogu da izađu. (The dogs fell into the trap and can't get out now.)
5. Kompanija je postavila *zamku* konkurenciji. (The company set a trap for the competition.)
6. Ribolovci su postavili *zamku* za ribu. (The fishermen set a trap for fish.)
7. Advokat je pokušao da postavi *zamku* svom klijentu. (The lawyer tried to set a trap for his client.)
8. Njegova prazna obećanja su *zamka* za neupućene ljude. (His empty promises are a trap for uninformed people.)
9. Kriminalci su postavili *zamku* policiji. (The criminals set a trap for the police.)
10. Turisti su se zaglavili u *zamci* snega na planini. (The tourists got stuck in a snow trap on the mountain.)